question: When did it last happen on the first ICU visit that the SaO2 of patient 10038999 was less than 96.0?
sql: SELECT chartevents.charttime FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10038999 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'o2 saturation pulseoxymetry' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND chartevents.valuenum < 96.0 ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: When did patient 10039708 have the minimum ferritin value in 11/2100 the last time?
sql: SELECT labevents.charttime FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10039708 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'ferritin' ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',labevents.charttime) = '2100-11' ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ASC, labevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: How many days have passed since patient 10021487 first took a pco2 lab test in this hospital encounter?
sql: SELECT 1 * ( strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J', labevents.charttime) ) FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'pco2' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021487 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Since 10/2100, was the heart rate for patient 10015931 normal?
sql: SELECT 1 - COUNT(*)>0 FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10015931 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'heart rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND chartevents.valuenum NOT BETWEEN heart_rate_lower AND heart_rate_upper AND strftime('%Y-%m',chartevents.charttime) >= '2100-10'

question: Has there been any microbiology test for patient 10006053 since 09/2100?
sql: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10006053 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100-09'

question: What is the top four most frequently prescribed drugs that were prescribed to patients within the same month after being diagnosed with other psoriasis in 2100?
sql: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other psoriasis' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4

question: What are the top three commonly ordered lab tests for patients 20s?
sql: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T1.itemid FROM ( SELECT labevents.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 ) GROUP BY labevents.itemid ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3 )

question: Which were the four most frequent specimens tested since 1 year ago?
sql: SELECT T1.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM microbiologyevents WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') GROUP BY microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4

question: What amount of pregabalin had been prescribed to patient 10020944 in total during the first hospital visit?
sql: SELECT SUM(prescriptions.dose_val_rx) FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10020944 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND prescriptions.drug = 'pregabalin'

question: How much does patient 10002495's troponin t differ from the last value measured on the last hospital visit compared to the second to last value measured on the last hospital visit?
sql: SELECT ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10002495 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'troponin t' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10002495 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'troponin t' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 )

question: What is the 3-month survival rate of patients who received alteplase treatment following a other psychotic disorder not due to a substance or known physiological condition diagnosis?
sql: SELECT AVG(C1) FROM ( SELECT ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T3.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT T1.subject_id, T1.charttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other psychotic disorder not due to a substance or known physiological condition' ) AND strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'alteplase' GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MAX(prescriptions.starttime) = prescriptions.starttime ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime ) AS T3 JOIN patients ON T3.subject_id = patients.subject_id )

question: What was the admission type during patient 10020740's first hospital visit?
sql: SELECT admissions.admission_type FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10020740 AND strftime('%Y',admissions.admittime) = '2100' ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Among patients diagnosed with hemoperitoneum since 2100, what were the top three most frequent microbiology tests conducted in the same hospital visit?
sql: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hemoperitoneum' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: Has there been any organism found in the last serology/blood test of patient 10007928?
sql: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007928 ) AND microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc = 'serology/blood' AND microbiologyevents.org_name IS NOT NULL ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: What treatment did patient 10019777 receive two or more times during their first hospital visit?
sql: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, COUNT( procedures_icd.charttime ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10019777 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 >= 2 )

question: When did patient 10031757 last take his or her swab microbiology test since 02/2100?
sql: SELECT microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031757 ) AND microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc = 'swab' AND strftime('%Y-%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100-02' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: What is patient 10037975's average value for potassium, whole blood in 02/2100?

question: How many hours has it been since patient 10018081's last diagnosis of unspecified essential hypertension on this hospital visit?

question: Count the total number of hospital visits of patient 10003400 last year.

question: Tell me the 6-month survival rate of patients who were diagnosed with microscopic hematuria and then given phytonadione.
sql: SELECT AVG(C1) FROM ( SELECT ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T3.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT T1.subject_id, T1.charttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'microscopic hematuria' ) AND strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'phytonadione' GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MAX(prescriptions.starttime) = prescriptions.starttime ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime ) AS T3 JOIN patients ON T3.subject_id = patients.subject_id )

question: What was the first potassium, whole blood lab result for patient 10018423?

question: Please provide the top three most common treatments.

question: Since patient 10018081's last stay in careunit trauma sicu (tsicu) on the current hospital encounter, how many days have passed?

question: What are the five most frequently ordered medications for patients diagnosed with gastro-esophageal reflux disease without esophagitis previously in the same hospital encounter, in 2100?
sql: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'gastro-esophageal reflux disease without esophagitis' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5

question: Find the number of people diagnosed with do not resuscitate status in 2100.

question: First time patient 10016742 was prescribed a drug in 08/this year?

question: What was the name of the insurance of patient 10006053 on their last hospital visit?

question: When is the first time patient 10004235 has had the maximum diastolic blood pressure during their last ICU stay?

question: Was patient 10029291 taken a lab test of ck-mb index on their first hospital encounter?

question: How much is patient 10027602's change of weight last measured on the first hospital visit compared to the first value measured on the first hospital visit?
sql: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )

question: Tell me the change in the heart rate of patient 10010471 last measured on the first ICU visit compared to the value first measured on the first ICU visit?
sql: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10010471 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'heart rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10010471 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'heart rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )

question: Tell me the percentile of the urea nitrogen value of 38.0 among patients of the same age as patient 10035185 in their first hospital visit?
sql: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'urea nitrogen' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10035185 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 38.0

question: What were the top three frequent diagnoses that patients received during the same month after undergoing the resection of vessel with replacement, thoracic vessels procedure in 2100?
sql: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'resection of vessel with replacement, thoracic vessels' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )

question: When was the first hospital admission of patient 10007795 who was admitted via transfer from hospital?
sql: SELECT admissions.admittime FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007795 AND admissions.admission_location = 'transfer from hospital' AND strftime('%Y',admissions.admittime) >= '2100' ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Get the total amount of or packed rbc intake that patient 10039831 received since 10/06/2100.

question: What are the five most frequently given diagnoses for the patients who had previously received laparoscopic partial cholecystectomy within 2 months, since 1 year ago?
sql: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'laparoscopic partial cholecystectomy' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )

question: How much does the systolic blood pressure of patient 10037975 change second measured on the first ICU visit compared to the first value measured on the first ICU visit?
sql: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10037975 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure systolic' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10037975 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure systolic' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )

question: Retrieve the top three most common diagnoses for patients with age in their 50s since 2100.
sql: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3 )

question: Since 04/2100, when was the last microbiology test conducted for patient 10001725?
sql: SELECT microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10001725 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100-04' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: Pull up the top four most frequent treatments that were delivered to patients during the same month after they received open reduction of fracture with internal fixation, humerus.
sql: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'open reduction of fracture with internal fixation, humerus' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

question: What's the admission time for patient 10038999 at the hospital in this year?

question: Could you tell me the top four most frequent treatments that were administered to patients during the same hospital encounter after they had fluoroscopy of right heart using other contrast since 2100?
sql: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'fluoroscopy of right heart using other contrast' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

question: Can I know the 3-month survival rate of patients diagnosed with subdural hemorrhage following injury without mention of open intracranial wound, with no loss of consciousness who were then prescribed phenobarbital?
sql: SELECT AVG(C1) FROM ( SELECT ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T3.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT T1.subject_id, T1.charttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'subdural hemorrhage following injury without mention of open intracranial wound, with no loss of consciousness' ) AND strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'phenobarbital' GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MAX(prescriptions.starttime) = prescriptions.starttime ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime ) AS T3 JOIN patients ON T3.subject_id = patients.subject_id )

question: Give me the details of the time patient 10020740 was admitted to the hospital in 2100.

question: What are the three most commonly used procedures for patients who had received other incision with drainage of skin and subcutaneous tissue previously in the same month, in this year?
sql: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other incision with drainage of skin and subcutaneous tissue' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )

question: What treatment did patient 10015860 receive two or more times in the last hospital visit?

question: Tell me the four most prevalent surgeries that patients underwent during the same month after having a percutaneous abdominal drainage.

question: What were the four most commonly conducted lab tests during the same month for patients who had a other skin graft to other sites procedure during this year?
sql: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other skin graft to other sites' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(labevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

question: Can you provide the top five most frequent lab tests that within the same month took place after patients had alcohol detoxification in 2100?

question: How many days have gone by since the last instance patient 10039831 had a or colloid intake input in the current ICU encounter?

question: Show me the difference between patient 10038999's total input and output on 05/31/this year.

question: What was the name of a drug that patient 10005817 was prescribed within 2 days after being diagnosed with chronic airway obstruction, not elsewhere classified throughout this month?

question: What are the five frequent input events since 1 year ago?
sql: SELECT d_items.label FROM d_items WHERE d_items.itemid IN ( SELECT T1.itemid FROM ( SELECT inputevents.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM inputevents WHERE datetime(inputevents.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') GROUP BY inputevents.itemid ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )

question: Did patient 10029291 undergo a ultrasonography of superior vena cava, guidance treatment in the first hospital visit?
sql: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'ultrasonography of superior vena cava, guidance' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10029291 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 )

question: Which five microbiology tests were most frequent for patients diagnosed with noncompliance with renal dialysis within 2 months?
sql: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'noncompliance with renal dialysis' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5

question: Which drug was prescribed to patient 10020306 for the first time since 13 months ago?
sql: SELECT prescriptions.drug FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10020306 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-13 month') ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: How much is the diagnosis price for candidiasis of mouth?

question: How many prescriptions for quinidine gluconate e.r. were given since 1 year ago?

question: Can you list the top four most common diagnoses for patients aged 20s in 2100?
sql: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4 )

question: What are the top five most frequent specimens tested among patients who received fluoroscopy of right heart using other contrast before within 2 months since 1 year ago?
sql: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'fluoroscopy of right heart using other contrast' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5

question: Count the current patients who belong to the 20s age group.
sql: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.subject_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.dischtime IS NULL AND admissions.age BETWEEN 20 AND 29

question: Since 2100, how many patients were given glucose gel within the same month after receiving a change feeding device in lower intestinal tract, external approach procedure?
sql: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'change feeding device in lower intestinal tract, external approach' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'glucose gel' AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month')

question: Calculate the number of patients who were given acetaminophen prescription within 2 months following their drainage of pancreatic cyst by catheter.
sql: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'drainage of pancreatic cyst by catheter' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'acetaminophen' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month')

question: How many hours have elapsed since patient 10039831 received his creatinine lab test for the first time on this hospital encounter?
sql: SELECT 24 * ( strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J', labevents.charttime) ) FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'creatinine' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10039831 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: In 2100, what were the top three most frequent lab tests conducted on patients during the same hospital encounter following a diagnosis of personal history of malignant neoplasm of other gastrointestinal tract?
sql: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'personal history of malignant neoplasm of other gastrointestinal tract' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )

question: How many days was the first hospital stay of patient 10019777 in the ICU?

question: How many times did patient 10021938 have an ICU admission in 2100?

question: Gather the total output since 10/05/2100 for patient 10007058.

question: How much does the heart rate of patient 10014729 change last measured on the first ICU visit compared to the first value measured on the first ICU visit?
sql: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10014729 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'heart rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10014729 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'heart rate' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )

question: What are the three most frequently tested specimens for patients who were previously diagnosed with encounter for attention to other artificial openings of digestive tract within 2 months?

question: What is the percentile of 2.71 in the laboratory red blood cells test given the same age as patient 10038081 during the last hospital visit?

question: What was patient 10027602's last prescribed time for bisacodyl during this month?

question: How many patients in 2100 were lidocaine 5% patch prescribed during the same month after undergoing restriction of left internal carotid artery with intraluminal device, percutaneous approach treatment?
sql: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'restriction of left internal carotid artery with intraluminal device, percutaneous approach' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'lidocaine 5% patch' AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month')

question: What are the five most usual lab tests for patients in their 40s in 2100?
sql: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T1.itemid FROM ( SELECT labevents.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 ) AND strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) = '2100' GROUP BY labevents.itemid ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )

question: What organism was found during the first urine test of patient 10037861 since 05/2100?

question: Can I know the 3-month survival rate of patients diagnosed with unspecified atrial fibrillation who were then prescribed rifaximin?
sql: SELECT AVG(C1) FROM ( SELECT ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T3.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT T1.subject_id, T1.charttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified atrial fibrillation' ) AND strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'rifaximin' GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MAX(prescriptions.starttime) = prescriptions.starttime ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime ) AS T3 JOIN patients ON T3.subject_id = patients.subject_id )

question: What was the last amount of ibuprofen suspension that was prescribed to patient 10014078 on the last hospital stay?

question: For the patients in their 60 or above since 1 year ago, which are the top five most frequently undergone procedures?

question: For patients that were given plasmalyte since 2100, what are the top five drugs that they were prescribed afterwards in the same month?

question: What does it cost to have catheter based invasive electrophysiologic testing?

question: Since 2100, has patient 10015931 received a encounter for examination for normal comparison and control in clinical research program diagnosis?

question: Calculate the total number of diagnostic ultrasound of abdomen and retroperitoneum cases.

question: What was the name of the microbiology test that patient 10008454 received last in this month?

question: What was the maximum value of pt on patient 10004235 in their last hospital encounter?

question: Show me the top five most common input events since 1 year ago.
sql: SELECT d_items.label FROM d_items WHERE d_items.itemid IN ( SELECT T1.itemid FROM ( SELECT inputevents.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM inputevents WHERE datetime(inputevents.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') GROUP BY inputevents.itemid ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )

question: What was the name of the diagnosis that patient 10006580 received last since 1 year ago?
sql: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10006580 ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ORDER BY diagnoses_icd.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 )

question: What was the name of the drug, which was prescribed to patient 10022041 last on the first hospital stay?

question: For patients who had reposition left maxilla with external fixation device, percutaneous approach since 1 year ago, could you tell me the three most common lab tests they had during the same month afterwards?
sql: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'reposition left maxilla with external fixation device, percutaneous approach' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(labevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )

question: How much do I need to pay for a procedure called drainage of pericardial cavity with drainage device, percutaneous approach?
sql: SELECT DISTINCT cost.cost FROM cost WHERE cost.event_type = 'procedures_icd' AND cost.event_id IN ( SELECT procedures_icd.row_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'drainage of pericardial cavity with drainage device, percutaneous approach' ) )

question: How many patients since 1 year ago had angiocardiography of left heart structures two times?

question: When was the last pt test that patient 10027445 received during the last hospital visit?

question: What drug was first prescribed to patient 10007818 via replace in the first hospital encounter?

question: Tell me patient 10021487's total tf residual output amount on 12/16/2100.
sql: SELECT SUM(outputevents.value) FROM outputevents WHERE outputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021487 ) ) AND outputevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'tf residual' AND d_items.linksto = 'outputevents' ) AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',outputevents.charttime) = '2100-12-16'

question: In this year, what are the top three commonly taken lab tests for patients aged 50s?
sql: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T1.itemid FROM ( SELECT labevents.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 ) AND datetime(labevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') GROUP BY labevents.itemid ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3 )

question: What were the top three most frequent specimens tested?
sql: SELECT T1.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM microbiologyevents GROUP BY microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3

question: What are the top four drugs that were prescribed to patients during the same month after they were prescribed vecuronium bromide during this year?
sql: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'vecuronium bromide' AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.starttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.starttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4

question: Throughout this year, what was the admission time of patient 10020187 at the hospital?

question: What medicine was prescribed to 10031404 during the same hospital visit after their drainage of pericardial cavity, percutaneous approach?
sql: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'drainage of pericardial cavity, percutaneous approach' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031404 ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031404 ) ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime

question: How many hours have passed from the time when patient 10018081 was admitted to the ICU?

question: Can you provide the monthly minimum amount of magnesium sulfate (bolus) that patient 10005817 received since 12/06/2100?

question: Retrieve the top five most frequently tested specimens that patients took in the same hospital visit after being diagnosed with chronic lymphocytic leukemia of b-cell type not having achieved remission.
sql: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'chronic lymphocytic leukemia of b-cell type not having achieved remission' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5

question: When was the first time that the heart rate readings of patient 10010471 were recorded on this month/19?

question: What is the percentile of 186.0 of glucose in a lab test for the same age of patient 10015931 in the last hospital visit?

question: Tell me the top five most frequent lab tests that patients took during the same month after being diagnosed with insomnia, unspecified since 2100.
sql: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'insomnia, unspecified' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )

sql: SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10003046 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure systolic' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: How many patients received metformin (glucophage) throughout this year?
sql: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.subject_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'metformin (glucophage)' AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') )

question: How many patients in the previous year received central venous catheter placement with guidance within the same month after they were diagnosed with family history of malignant neoplasm of trachea, bronchus, and lung?
sql: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'family history of malignant neoplasm of trachea, bronchus, and lung' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'central venous catheter placement with guidance' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month')

question: Could you calculate the difference between the total input and output of patient 10021666 since 03/27/2100?
sql: SELECT ( SELECT SUM(inputevents.totalamount) FROM inputevents WHERE inputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021666 ) ) AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',inputevents.starttime) >= '2100-03-27' ) - ( SELECT SUM(outputevents.value) FROM outputevents WHERE outputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021666 ) ) AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',outputevents.charttime) >= '2100-03-27' )

question: On the last hospital visit, did patient 10022041 receive any diagnoses?
sql: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10022041 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 )

question: How many hours has it been since patient 10004733's first stay in the careunit neurology on the current hospital visit?
sql: SELECT 24 * ( strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J', transfers.intime) ) FROM transfers WHERE transfers.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004733 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) AND transfers.careunit = 'neurology' ORDER BY transfers.intime ASC LIMIT 1

question: How many patients last year had endoscopic control of gastric or duodenal bleeding two times?
sql: SELECT COUNT(T1.subject_id) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, COUNT(*) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'endoscopic control of gastric or duodenal bleeding' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') GROUP BY admissions.subject_id ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 = 2

question: When did patient 10022880 first receive his or her chloride lab test in 04/this year?
sql: SELECT labevents.charttime FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'chloride' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10022880 ) AND datetime(labevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',labevents.charttime) = '04' ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Give me the number of hospital visits patient 10018501 made.
sql: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT admissions.hadm_id ) FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018501

question: What were the top four frequent input events in 2100?
sql: SELECT d_items.label FROM d_items WHERE d_items.itemid IN ( SELECT T1.itemid FROM ( SELECT inputevents.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM inputevents WHERE strftime('%Y',inputevents.starttime) = '2100' GROUP BY inputevents.itemid ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4 )

question: Tell me the difference in the creatinine value for patient 10019568 second measured on the last hospital visit compared to the first value measured on the last hospital visit?
sql: SELECT ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10019568 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'creatinine' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) - ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10019568 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'creatinine' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )

question: What was the name of the drug, which patient 10012853 was prescribed in the same day after being diagnosed with peripheral vascular disease, unspecified on their last hospital visit?
sql: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.charttime, diagnoses_icd.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10012853 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'peripheral vascular disease, unspecified' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10012853 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of day') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of day')

question: What microbiology test was given to patient 10004235 for the first time during the first hospital encounter?
sql: SELECT microbiologyevents.test_name FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004235 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Can you list the drug that patient 10021118 was last prescribed in 12/2100?
sql: SELECT prescriptions.drug FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021118 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-12' ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: Has there been any organism found since 01/2100 in the last abscess test of patient 10007795?
sql: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10007795 ) AND microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc = 'abscess' AND microbiologyevents.org_name IS NOT NULL AND strftime('%Y-%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100-01' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: What are the four commonly tested specimens for patients diagnosed with anoxic brain damage, not elsewhere classified previously during the same hospital visit, since 1 year ago?
sql: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'anoxic brain damage, not elsewhere classified' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4

question: Since 03/20/2100, when was the first input of patient 10014354?
sql: SELECT inputevents.starttime FROM inputevents WHERE inputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10014354 ) ) AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',inputevents.starttime) >= '2100-03-20' ORDER BY inputevents.starttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: What was the admission type during patient 10018423's first hospital visit?
sql: SELECT admissions.admission_type FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018423 AND strftime('%Y',admissions.admittime) = '2100' ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1

question: What was the total number of drugs prescribed to patient 10009628 in 09/this year?
sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10009628 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '09'

question: When did patient 10022041 first get mrsa screen microbiology test in 06/this year?
sql: SELECT microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10022041 ) AND microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc = 'mrsa screen' AND datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '06' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Calculate the number of patients who were given spironolactone prescription within the same hospital visit following their percutaneous abdominal drainage in the previous year.
sql: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'percutaneous abdominal drainage' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'spironolactone' AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id

question: What was the name of the medicine that was prescribed to patient 10027602 in the same hospital encounter after receiving the endovascular (total) embolization or occlusion of head and neck vessels procedure since 3 months ago?
sql: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'endovascular (total) embolization or occlusion of head and neck vessels' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-3 month') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-3 month') ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime

question: What are the four most commonly prescribed treatments for patients previously diagnosed with long term (current) use of opiate analgesic during the same hospital visit since 2100?
sql: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'long term (current) use of opiate analgesic' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

question: For the first time, how much acetaminophen iv was prescribed to patient 10031757?
sql: SELECT prescriptions.dose_val_rx FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10031757 ) AND prescriptions.drug = 'acetaminophen iv' ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: For the first time, in their last hospital encounter, how much lidocaine jelly 2% (urojet) was prescribed to patient 10002495?

question: What's the gender of patient 10014078?
sql: SELECT patients.gender FROM patients WHERE patients.subject_id = 10014078

question: What is the price of the drug vitamin e?

question: Tell me the insurance plan for patient 10023239 during the first hospital visit.
sql: SELECT admissions.insurance FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10023239 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1

question: What was the name of the medication that was prescribed to patient 10005817 within the same hospital visit after receiving a single internal mammary-coronary artery bypass procedure since 12/2100?
sql: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'single internal mammary-coronary artery bypass' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10005817 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100-12' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10005817 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-12' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime

question: Which four microbiology tests were most frequent for patients diagnosed with supermarket, store or market as the place of occurrence of the external cause during the same month?
sql: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'supermarket, store or market as the place of occurrence of the external cause' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4

question: During their first hospital visit, was patient 10001217 in the emergency room?
sql: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10001217 AND admissions.admission_location = 'emergency room' AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1

question: What is the maximum overall hospital cost when it includes a lactate dehydrogenase, pleural lab test since 2100?
sql: SELECT MAX(T1.C1) FROM ( SELECT SUM(cost.cost) AS C1 FROM cost WHERE cost.hadm_id IN ( SELECT labevents.hadm_id FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'lactate dehydrogenase, pleural' ) ) AND strftime('%Y',cost.chargetime) >= '2100' GROUP BY cost.hadm_id ) AS T1

question: Has patient 10004733 got a central venous catheter placement with guidance treatment during this hospital visit?
sql: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'central venous catheter placement with guidance' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004733 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL )

question: Which diagnosis did patient 10011398 get for the last time during the first hospital encounter?
sql: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10011398 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ORDER BY diagnoses_icd.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 )

question: Since 1 year ago, what were the three most commonly prescribed drugs within 2 months after the diagnosis of hypo-osmolality and hyponatremia?
sql: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hypo-osmolality and hyponatremia' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: Can you tell me the number of excision of right lower lung lobe, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic procedures in 2100?

question: On the first hospital encounter, when was the last time that patient 10031757 received a alkaline phosphatase lab test?

question: In 07/2100 did patient 10016742 undergo a creatinine, urine test?

question: What was the last medication patient 10038933 was prescribed via td on the first hospital encounter?

question: What is the average daily number of patients with acute on chronic diastolic heart failure in 2100?

question: What are the five most common diagnoses of people in their 60 or above?
sql: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age >= 60 ) GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 5 )

question: What are the four most commonly prescribed treatments for patients previously diagnosed with other and unspecified escherichia coli [e. coli] in the same month?
sql: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other and unspecified escherichia coli [e. coli]' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

question: What was the maximum value of heart rate of patient 10029291?

question: Was the value of the platelet count of patient 10036156 last measured on the last hospital visit greater than that first measured on the last hospital visit?

question: What is the total amount of gastric meds input that patient 10027602 received on 11/29/2100?
sql: SELECT SUM(inputevents.totalamount) FROM inputevents WHERE inputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10027602 ) ) AND inputevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'gastric meds' AND d_items.linksto = 'inputevents' ) AND strftime('%Y-%m-%d',inputevents.starttime) = '2100-11-29'

question: Give me the top five most frequent microbiology tests that patients were given after being diagnosed with secondary and unspecified malignant neoplasm of intra-abdominal lymph nodes within the same hospital visit in 2100.
sql: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'secondary and unspecified malignant neoplasm of intra-abdominal lymph nodes' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5

question: When did since 05/2100 patient 10000032 receive a microbiology test for the first time?
sql: SELECT microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10000032 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100-05' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Did patient 10013049 have oral gastric in 06/2100?
sql: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM outputevents WHERE outputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10013049 ) ) AND outputevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'oral gastric' AND d_items.linksto = 'outputevents' ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',outputevents.charttime) = '2100-06'

question: For patients who were given thoracoscopic decortication of lung, what are the top five most common lab tests that followed afterwards during the same month?
sql: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'thoracoscopic decortication of lung' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )

question: What are the three most frequently ordered medications since 2100?
sql: SELECT T1.drug FROM ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM prescriptions WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100' GROUP BY prescriptions.drug ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3

question: How much do I have to pay for a procedure called alcohol detoxification?

question: How many patients since 1 year ago were in the discharge lounge careunit?

question: What drug was patient 10018423 prescribed with within 2 days after undergoing excision of right internal mammary artery, percutaneous endoscopic approach?
sql: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'excision of right internal mammary artery, percutaneous endoscopic approach' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018423 ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018423 ) ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 day')

question: How many patients were treated with other excision or destruction of lesion or tissue of pancreas or pancreatic duct two or more times since 1 year ago?
sql: SELECT COUNT(T1.subject_id) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, COUNT(*) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other excision or destruction of lesion or tissue of pancreas or pancreatic duct' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') GROUP BY admissions.subject_id ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 >= 2
